1.1) Check general user info:
	USER@OMG:~$ cd Documents
	USER@OMG:~/Documents$ cat /etc/passwd | grep newone
	newone:x:1001:1001:Newest Onest,2,88008880088,791544,boo:/home newone: bin/bash



1.2) Check shadowed password:
	USER@OMG:~/Documents$ sudo cat /etc/shadow | grep newone
	newone:$y$j9T$UVnRbpdDnreTrimsgKTOu1$qo2oCvCuzKd5mm1na1QcfOoRpt2w5Ni9n6vu0nI8Ry0:20068:0:99999:7:::


1.3) Check group info:
	USER@OMG:~/Documents$  cat /etc/group | grep newone
	users:x:100:USER,newone
	newone:x:1001:



1.4) Deleting new user:
	USER@OMG:~/Documents$  sudo userdel -r newone
	userdel: newone mail spool (/var/mail/newone) not found




2) Group management:
	USER@OMG:~/Documents$ sudo groupadd newonegroup




2.1) Moving 'newmaksim' into newgroup:
	USER@OMG:~/Documents$ sudo usermod -g newonegroup newone
	


2.2) Adding 'newone' into newgsecondgroup but not deleting from newgroup:
	USER@OMG:~/Documents$ sudo groupadd newsecondgroup
	USER@OMG:~/Documents$ sudo usermod -aG newsecondgroup newone



2.3) Removing user from newsecondgroup:
	USER@OMG:~/Documents$  sudo gpasswd -d newone newsecondgroup
	Removing user newone from group newsecondgroup



