4) Modification of 'newone' now can execute sudo apt and adduser without pass:
	put in /etc/sudoers/ 'newone ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/apt, /usr/bin/useradd'
	USER@OMG:~/Documents$ su newone
	USER@OMG:~/Documents$ sudo apt update
